survey.name: Intro_instructions
label:
Thank you for taking the time to register your organisations response to Hurricane Melissa in Jamaica.
Please note that each submission should represent one single activity.

Data is aggregated at the community level, therefore, if your activity covers multiple communities, you will need to enter disaggregated figures for each community. A looping section in the form will guide you through this process.

If you encounter any issues while completing the form, please contact 5W Support Team at [melissa-5w-support@undac.org](mailto:melissa-5w-support@undac.org) for assistance.
